OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FHealth services are at "breaking
OL,7,Fpoint" as incidents of self-harm have
OL,8,Fmore than doubled at an immigration
OL,9,Fdetention centre which feels "like a
OL,10,Fprison", inspectors have warned.
OL,12,FFights and assaults on staff at Brook
OL,13,FHouse immigration removal centre had
OL,14,Fincreased more than five-fold since
OL,15,Fthe last inspectors' visit in 2022,
OL,16,Frising from 14 to 80 assaults and
OL,17,Feight to 50 fights, but inspectors
OL,18,Fsaid leaders were not using data
OL,19,Feffectively to understand the cause of
OL,20,Fit.
