OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FMore than a third of approximately 330
OL,7,Fdetainees at Brook House, near Gatwick
OL,8,FAirport in West Sussex, told officials
OL,9,Fthey had felt suicidal at the site at
OL,10,Fsome point and incidents of self-harm
OL,11,Fhad more than doubled to 12 a month
OL,12,Fsince the last inspection, the report
OL,13,Ffrom HM Chief Inspector of Prisons
OL,14,Ffound.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
