OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FChief inspector Charlie Taylor said:
OL,7,F"In this context, it was a matter of
OL,8,Fserious concern to find a
OL,9,Fdeterioration in health care
OL,10,Fprovision: the inadequacy of health
OL,11,Fservices was one of the biggest
OL,12,Fcomplaints from detainees and it was
OL,13,Fclear that the service was stretched
OL,14,Fto breaking point."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
