OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FThe concerns come as a man died in
OL,7,Fhospital after being detained at the
OL,8,Fcentre in November 2023 while another
OL,9,Fdetainee was discovered dead at Brook
OL,10,FHouse in what is believed to be
OL,11,Funnatural circumstances in October
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FThe latest inspection that took place
OL,15,Fover August 5-22 this year found a
OL,16,F"concerning and substantial rise" in
OL,17,Fviolence and self-harm while safety
OL,18,Fand respect had also declined.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
