OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FConcerns were also raised over
OL,7,Fstaffing, culture and morale of the
OL,8,Fhealth services team which was "not
OL,9,Fdelivering a good enough service" to
OL,10,Fdetainees, while inspectors
OL,11,Fhighlighted "pockets of immature and
OL,12,Funprofessional behaviour" from
OL,13,Foperational staff, half of whom had
OL,14,Fless than two years' experience in the
OL,15,Fjob.
OL,17,FDrugs at Brook House were also
OL,18,Fbecoming increasingly available but
OL,19,Fplanning and resources to tackle the
OL,20,Fproblem were "inadequate", the report
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
