OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FOn living conditions, Mr Taylor added:
OL,7,F"A longstanding and fundamental
OL,8,Fproblem was that all immigration
OL,9,Fdetainees at Brook House, who should
OL,10,Fbe held in relaxed conditions with
OL,11,Fminimal restrictions, were instead in
OL,12,Fan institution that looked and felt
OL,13,Flike a prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
