OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FMr Taylor said this was an
OL,7,F"unacceptably long time" to keep
OL,8,Fpeople in administrative detention and
OL,9,Fthe longer stays meant higher needs
OL,10,Fand frustrations of detainees.
OL,12,FHe added the average cumulative
OL,13,Fdetention, including before someone
OL,14,Fwas transferred to Brook House, was 78
OL,15,Fdays, which was "too long" as 58% of
OL,16,Fdetainees leaving the centre in the
OL,17,Flast six months were released into the
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
