OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FIn the last year, at least 20 people,
OL,7,Fincluding those assessed as
OL,8,Fvulnerable, had been released from the
OL,9,Fcentre homeless, the report added.
OL,11,FInspectors praised efforts to improve
OL,12,Factivities at Brook House and
OL,13,Fdiscovered there were more jobs and
OL,14,Fspaces for physical and recreational
OL,15,Factivities, while welfare work
OL,16,Fremained good despite the service
OL,17,Fbeing "fragile and understaffed".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
