OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FThe centre has been the subject of a
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry which found 19
OL,8,Fincidents of mistreatment against
OL,9,Fdetainees at the detention centre over
OL,10,Fa five-month period in 2017.
OL,12,FInquiry chair Kate Eves has called for
OL,13,Fa "reset" on an "inadequate"
OL,14,FGovernment response to her
OL,15,Frecommendations on preventing a repeat
OL,16,Fof the Brook House immigration centre
OL,17,Fscandal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
