OL,3,CHealth services at 'breaking point' at
OL,4,Cairport immigration centre
OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Frecognise standards need to improve
OL,8,Facross immigration detention
OL,9,Ffacilities, that is why we are taking
OL,10,Frobust action to improve conditions
OL,11,Fand safeguards, informed by the
OL,12,Ffindings of this report.
OL,14,F"We are reviewing current practices
OL,15,Faround preventing violence and use of
OL,16,Fforce within the site, and have
OL,17,Fintroduced a programme focused on
OL,18,Fimproving the overall culture, as well
OL,19,Fas a mentoring scheme for newly
OL,20,Frecruited officers."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
